column2: SELECT m.ra_#, m.dec_#, m.specObjID, S.ra, S.dec, S.specObjID, S.mjd, S.plate, S.fiberID, S.class, S.z, S.zErr, S.rChi2, S.velDisp, S.velDispErr, dbo.fgeturlfitsspectrum (S.specobjid) , G.extinction_r, G.petroMag_r, G.psfMag_r, G.psfMagErr_r, G.modelMag_u, G.modelMagErr_u, G.modelMag_g, G.modelMagErr_g, G.modelMag_r, G.modelMagErr_r, G.modelMag_i, G.modelMagErr_i, G.modelMag_z, G.modelMagErr_z, G.petroR5#_r, G.petroR9#_r INTO MyDB.chandra_matched_sdss_details3# FROM MyDB.chandra_matched_sdss_# AS m OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEQ (m.ra_#, m.dec_#, #) AS n LEFT JOIN SpecObj AS S ON n.ObjID = S.bestObjID LEFT JOIN SpecPhoto G ON S.specObjID = G.specObjID
